  "title": "Durability Visibility Options",
  "description": "A large number of settings for the visual appearance of the durability bar!",
  "body": "<center><h1> Durability Visibility Options</h1></center>\n<p align=\"center\"> <a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/durability_visibility_options\"> <img alt=\"modrinth\" height=\"56\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/@intergrav/devins-badges@3/assets/cozy/available/modrinth_vector.svg\"> </a> <a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/durability-visibility-options\"> <img alt=\"curseforge\" height=\"56\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/@intergrav/devins-badges@3/assets/cozy/available/curseforge_vector.svg\"> </a> </p> <p align=\"center\"> <a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/yacl\"> <img alt=\"yacl\" height=\"56\" src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Danrus1100/durability_visibility_options/refs/heads/dev/assets/YACL.svg\"> </a> </p> <p align=\"center\"> <a href=\"https://discord.gg/sBpHZUBebQ\"> <img alt=\"discord\" height=\"40\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/@intergrav/devins-badges@3/assets/compact/social/discord-singular_vector.svg\"> </a> </p>\n\n    Customize the durability display just the way you want it!\n    This mod gives you full control over how item durability is shown in Minecraft.\n\n<center><h1>🌟 Key Features</h1></center>\n\n- ✅ Toggle visibility for the bar and percentages\n- 🎨 Choose custom colors for both bar and text\n- 📐 Adjust the position of durability indicators\n- 🔍 Auto-hide bar/percentage when items are fully repaired or broken\n- 💾 Save and load user-defined presets\n<p align=\"center\"> <img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/a44c80125845f4bf54783314260a53930e90bb3d.jpeg\" alt=\"Settings Preview\" width=\"500\"/> <br/> <img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/50bfaa403db1e65143547f523364884b5e02fc23.png\" alt=\"Durability HUD Preview\" width=\"500\"/> </p>\n<center><h1>🛠️ Durability In-Game</h1></center>\n<p align=\"center\"> <img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/35330e9997aba42b7114c1ff21bc239521780c21.png\" alt=\"Durability Example 1\" width=\"400\"/> <img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/RPJED5Ye/images/06e78be0206559f4468bd63e0db5b7f86df267c4.png\" alt=\"Durability Example 2\" width=\"400\"/> </p>\n<center><h1>💡 Special Thanks</h1></center>\n\nHuge shoutout to inlitum — creator of Duraview, for inspiring this mod!\n<center><h1>🧩 Try My Other Mods</h1></center>\n<p align=\"center\"> <a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/destroy-item-white-list\"> <img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/a6dae3716505b7221af13b6f5f4aae1bcb71e028.png\" alt=\"Destroy Item White List\" width=\"287px\"/> </a> <a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/durability_visibility_options\"> <img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/8cae1332efddc92a0b627301f69521af24d1f934.png\" alt=\"Durability Visibility Options\" width=\"319px\"/> </a> <a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/rocket-utils\"> <img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/4c7829b3b82784717731ef0ef50d9c5ec89471cf.png\" alt=\"Rocket Utils\" width=\"223px\"/> </a> </p>",
